{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_38","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve ruled out the obvious reflection gap: the generated-mappings class and its accessor methods are already registered. The remaining problem is that the mapping for `TestBeanTestCase` is empty at runtime, so I’m using the same pinned GraalVM JDK to inspect what `TestContextAotGenerator` would actually generate for that test case and then wiring that into the fixture if needed."}}
